OL,3,CGreggs warns conditions 'still tough'
OL,4,Cfor shoppers after slump in profits
OL,6,FGreggs has said it is "still tough out
OL,7,Fthere" for customers after it revealed
OL,8,Fa slump in profits for the past year.
OL,10,FHowever, boss Roisin Currie said that
OL,11,F"easing inflationary pressures" should
OL,12,Fboost consumer spending this year.
OL,14,FThe Newcastle-based firm said it has
OL,15,Fseen its cost inflation slow from
OL,16,Falmost 6% last year to around 3% this
OL,17,Fyear but is still witnessing cautious
OL,18,Fsentiment among shoppers.
OL,26,@nD@WOUoD@FO]sD@AOUsD@_O]
