PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1772892686
OL,3,CGreggs warns conditions 'still tough'
OL,4,Cfor shoppers after slump in profits
OL,6,FMs Currie told the Press Association:
OL,7,F"We have come into 2026 planning for
OL,8,Fanother challenging year.
OL,10,F"When you look at consumer confidence
OL,11,Fand disposable income you can see that
OL,12,Fthe backdrop is still tough out there."
OL,14,FThe high street bakery chain, well
OL,15,Fknown for its sausage rolls and steak
OL,16,Fbakes, reported on Tuesday (3 March) a
OL,17,Fslowdown in sales growth over the
OL,18,Fstart of the new year.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUtD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
