PN,42903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1772892686
OL,3,CGreggs warns conditions 'still tough'
OL,4,Cfor shoppers after slump in profits
OL,6,FNevertheless, the retail business,
OL,7,Fwhich employs more than 33,000 people,
OL,8,Fstressed that it has been "resilient"
OL,9,Fin the face of a "challenging market".
OL,11,FOver the past year, Greggs has come
OL,12,Funder pressure from cautious shoppers
OL,13,Faffected by the rising cost-of-living,
OL,14,Fhigher tax and labour costs, and the
OL,15,Fgrowing use of weight-loss treatments.
OL,17,FHowever, the chief executive indicated
OL,18,Fthat there are "green shoots" and some
OL,19,Fof these challenges could ease over
OL,20,Fthe current year.
OL,26,@pD@[OUpD@eO]qD@ROUqD@eO]zD@POUzD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
