PN,42904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1772892686
OL,3,CGreggs warns conditions 'still tough'
OL,4,Cfor shoppers after slump in profits
OL,6,FShe said: "Looking into 2026, easing
OL,7,Finflationary pressures should provide
OL,8,Fsome support to consumer spending and
OL,9,Fdemand for convenient food-on-the-go
OL,10,Fcontinues to underpin the market."
OL,12,FOn Tuesday, Greggs reported that
OL,13,Fstatutory pre-tax profits fell by
OL,14,F17.9% to #167.4 million for the year
OL,15,Fto December 27, compared with a year
OL,16,Fearlier.
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
