PN,42905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1772892686
OL,3,CGreggs warns conditions 'still tough'
OL,4,Cfor shoppers after slump in profits
OL,6,FIt said the drop in profits was partly
OL,7,Flinked to the tough market backdrop
OL,8,Fand a "spell of particularly hot
OL,9,Fweather" which knocked high street
OL,10,Ffootfall.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FIt also told shareholders that total
OL,18,Fsales grew by 6.8% to #2.15 billion
OL,19,Fover the year, with like-for-like
OL,20,Fgrowth also buoyed by its continued
OL,21,Fstore opening programme.
OL,26,@pD@GOUqD@HO]
