PN,42906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1772892686
OL,3,CGreggs warns conditions 'still tough'
OL,4,Cfor shoppers after slump in profits
OL,6,FGreggs said it had 121 net store
OL,7,Fopenings in 2025, expanding its shop
OL,8,Festate to 2,739 locations by the end
OL,9,Fof the year.
OL,11,FIt is targeting around 120 further
OL,12,Fopenings this year as it highlighted
OL,13,Fambitions to grow to "significantly
OL,14,Fmore than 3,000 UK shops over longer
OL,15,Fterm".
OL,17,FSales growth was also supported by the
OL,18,Fexpansion of its delivery business and
OL,19,Fan increase in evening trade.
OL,26,@uD@VOUwD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/7
