PN,42907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1772892686
OL,3,CGreggs warns conditions 'still tough'
OL,4,Cfor shoppers after slump in profits
OL,6,FMore recently, like-for-like sales
OL,7,Facross its managed shops grew by 1.6%
OL,8,Fover the first nine weeks of 2026,
OL,9,Fwith total sales up 6.3% on the back
OL,10,Fof store openings.
